{
  "stem": "14091.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And lots of laughter, lots of happiness.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And because the city was small, all the people there were involved with each other, either related or just good friends.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember the most beautiful, beautiful childhood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was constantly caressed by everybody, especially my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I loved her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The city was located-- we had a river.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I loved to play in this river and swim and play and run and-- [SIGHS] when I think of it now, I, I am thinking that this was really the most beautiful time in my life.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the memories are so vivid, so beautiful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But this was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] abrupted when the-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] when the world war started.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The Germans attacked Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And after a very short time, instead of the Germans, the Russians came.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our town, it was-- we had two synagogues.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was Ashkanazi and it was Sephardim.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We, we loved to belong to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We weren't very religious, but we were traditional.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Holidays were observed and with lots and lots of people coming and going.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In our house, because it was such a large home, my mother also helped out for very poor people to get married and they would be married in our house.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember we had the huge chair where the brides would be seated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We also had in our house a-- once, like in once a month or so, it would be a movies.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They would come, and we would watch movies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Also it would be gathering socially for young people, because, as I say, it was a very, very large room.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Our home had very big rooms and many.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the back of our house, there was another house.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
